wdi-DT.NFL.BLAT.CD.def: Bilateral debt includes loans from governments and their agencies (including central banks), loans from autonomous bodies, and direct loans from official export credit agencies. Net flows (or net lending or net disbursements) received by the borrower during the year are disbursements minus principal repayments. Data are in current U.S. dollars.
wdi-DT.NFL.BLAT.CD.name: Net financial flows
